body_html:
@gujinghui @jgong5 This is awesome! There are two things that I'm interested in.

  • Do we have some benchmark numbers between the IDEEPOperators and our old MLKOperators?
  • Could you elaborate a bit more on "subgraph level optimization"? Are there any examples that I can take a look?
    Thanks.

Code-wise, maybe it makes more sense to put it in caffe2/contrib? Also adding @Yangqing to take a look.
